headline: Trane Technologies Completes Acquisition of BrainBox AI
summary: SWORDS, Ireland, January 03, 2025--Trane Technologies (NYSE: TT), a global climate innovator, announced that it has completed the acquisition of BrainBox AI, a pioneer in autonomous HVAC controls and generative Artificial Intelligence (AI) building technology. The acquisition was previously announced in a press release on December 18, 2024.
